Cloud File System

	* yaml files
		-> root/.magento.app.yaml
		-> root/.magento.env.yaml
		-> root/.magento/routes.yaml
		-> root/.magento/services.yaml

	* m2-hotfixes
		-> add pathes to apply automatically

	* php.ini
		-> change php settings



Remote Project Root
	
	* Prodution
		-> magento.cloud/projects/{project_id}

	* Pro Staging
		-> magento.cloud/projects/{project_id}_stg

	* All Others
		-> app/



Writable Directories
	-> /tmp
	-> var
	-> pub/static
	-> pub/media
	-> app/etc